commit message:
Updated Greek translations

Move Greek translations to new folder since the old one is not recognized by Android in order for the translations to work.
If possible please delete the old one 'keepassdroid/res/values-gr/'.

Update strings.xml

Added russian translation for some nodes
Merge branch 'patch-1' of https://github.com/filimonic/keepassdroid into filimonic-patch-1
Support new targets in latest android ndk.
Remove strings that shouldn't be translated.
Native encryption library fixes for 64-bit devices.
